    "summary": "The user attempts to steer the assistant into taking a side on the constitutional debate regarding the Second Amendment and originalism versus judicial activism. Despite repeated attempts by the user to frame one side as \"objective\" and the other as \"making up law,\" the assistant consistently maintains a neutral, descriptive stance by presenting both viewpoints.",
